# Bayesian Theorem

```{python}

import numpy.random as rs_rv

```

```{python}

rs_rv.standard_normal(size = 10)
rs_rv.standard_normal(size = (10, 2))    # 10 by 2 matrix
rs_rv.choice(
  a = [0, 1], 
  size = 100, 
  replace= True, 
  p = [0.9, 0.1]
)


```


